><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flowing Thought Items?</span><hr size=1> Btw we got a FT6 item the other night from the creator, so there's items 1 though 6 now.   The only suckky thing about the item is that no Dark Elfs could use it, what a rip.<br><br>-Sert out<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/usertaintkell.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sertain TKell</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/6/02 8:47:57 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Flowing Thought Items?</span><hr size=1> Anyway, I though I would answer you question, take a look at my dream gear and you'll see all the items that are availble with FT on them minus the new shield with FT6 on it and the gloves - Geomantic Fingers of Focus - FT3.<br><br><br><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=82042">www.magelo.com/eq_view_pr...?num=82042</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>There are a few more FT1 items out there, but for the most part, that the best of them.<br><br>-Sert out<br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/uyellowhat7.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Yellowhat7</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/6/02 1:10:24 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> question2</span><hr size=1> Ok better question, any FT items a lvl 40 wizard has a chance to get a hold of?  With some help ofcourse <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=milaru>Milaru</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Sorcerer</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/6/02 1:15:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: question2</span><hr size=1> how much help?  a nice number of 60s, a few, a bunch of level 40s?  none. <p><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=80058" target="_blank"><img src="http://web.tampabay.rr.com/eqsite/Milaru.jpg" border="0"></a> </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ubonegruel.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bonegruel</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Evoker</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(2/8/02 10:05:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: question2</span><hr size=1> None that are really doable in the low 40's sorry.  <br><br>But what a 40'ish wizard can do is do the first 3 shawl quests, and get working on their tailoring.   By the time tailoring is at 158, you should be level 50 or so, at which stage you can work on completing the rest of the quest for the coldain prayer shawl.  At 50 you will need a solid group to get some of the components, but if you master tailoring (and a few other tradeskills) then you've done 90% of the work.  7th Prayer shawl = shoulder slot, FT1, +7 int +7 Fr/cold/magic resists, +7 to some other stats.  <br><br>There are a couple of pieces in the game are arguably better than the 7th shawl.... but chances if you get the shawl you'll never replace it.  Not to mention that further quests in the series are supposedly going to be implented one day, with an end-result that will surely be uber by anyone's standards. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showPrevMessage?topicID=13.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showNextMessage?topicID=13.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=13.topic&index=5><img src=http://www.graffe.com/messageboard/add_reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.emailToFriend?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.threadControl?topicID=13.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub23.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm36.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=13.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub2